<!--**********************************************************************
    *                                                                    *
    *                        S1000D Issue 2                              *
    *                SGML Document Type Definition                       *
    *                                                                    *
    *                     Release Version 2.2                            *
    *                       Date: 2005-05-01                             *
    *                                                                    *
    * Amendment:-                                                        *
    * 1. CPF 2004-32US: New public identifier.                           *
    * 2. CPF 2004-03SE: Rename element <closeup> to <closereqs>. Change  *
    *                   its content model to include element <reqconds>  *
    *                   only and remove inclusion of <figure>, <foldout> *
    *                   and <table>.                                     *
    *                                                                    *
    * Typical invocation:-                                               *
    * <!ENTITY % CLOSEREQ                                                *
    *   PUBLIC "-//S1000D//ELEMENTS Closeup Requirements 20050501//EN" > *
    * %CLOSEREQ;                                                         *
    ********************************************************************** -->


<!--**********************************************************************
    *  Define Element closereqs (Close up requirements) containing:-     *
    *  reqconds   - Mandatory  Single     contains noconds, reqcond,     *
    *                                              reqcondm, reqcontp.   *
    *@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@*
    * Attribute(s):-                                                     *
    *  Attribute Definition list stored in entity %bodyatt;              *
    ********************************************************************** -->

<!ELEMENT closereqs - O (reqconds) >
<!ATTLIST closereqs
            %bodyatt; >
<!-- Element <closeup> renamed to <closereqs>, content model changed and
     inclusion of <figure>, <foldout>, <table> removed. -->
